---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About" description="About Jason Marsh — developer, technologist, assistive technology specialist.">
  <h1>About</h1>

  <div class="about-intro">
    <img src="/jason.jpg" alt="Jason Marsh" class="about-photo" width="200" height="200" />
    <div class="prose">
    <p>
      I'm Jason — a developer and technologist based in Duluth, Minnesota, with 13+
      years in IT. I direct technology at a nonprofit where I manage infrastructure,
      lead assistive technology services, and run an AT lending library — serving
      older adults, people with disabilities, and anyone who needs help navigating
      technology. I hold an Assistive Technology Applications
      Certificate from CSUN.
    </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="prose">
    <p>
      Outside of that role, I build production software as a solo developer. I've
      shipped <a href="/projects/mealdeck/">a meal planning app</a> with AI-powered
      recipe adaptation, <a href="/projects/petfeedr/">an automated pet feeder</a>
      running on a Raspberry Pi, <a href="/projects/radiogridxl/">an accessibility-first
      radio streaming app</a> now deployed to older adults at my organization, and
      <a href="/projects/echoetcher/">a voice-to-notes pipeline</a> that turns audio
      memos into structured Markdown. My primary stack is
      Node.js, SQLite, and vanilla JavaScript, with Python for machine learning and
      automation. Claude is a core part of how I build — not a crutch, but a
      building partner.
    </p>

    <p>
      I came to software through art — a B.S. in Game Art & Design, a stint as a
      concept artist doing noir-style western illustrations, and a lot of self-teaching.
      That background shows up in how I approach problems: I think visually, I design
      for the people using the thing, and I ship the whole product — not just the backend.
    </p>

    <p>
      For a more detailed look at my experience and skills, check out my <a href="/resume/">resume</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>Get in touch</h2>

    <p>
      I'm always interested in conversations about AI engineering, assistive technology,
      or hard problems worth solving. If my work resonates, I'd like to hear from you.
    </p>

    <ul>
      <li>Email: <a href="mailto:regularlyjason@icloud.com">regularlyjason@icloud.com</a></li>
      <li>LinkedIn: <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jason-marsh">jason-marsh</a></li>
      <li>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/Minimalistic">Minimalistic</a></li>
      <li>Art: <a href="https://jasonhmarsh.artstation.com">ArtStation</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .about-intro {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .about-photo {
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    object-fit: cover;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }
  .about-intro .prose p {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .about-intro {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .about-photo {
      width: 160px;
      height: 160px;
    }
  }
</style>
